118
00:14:52,722 --> 00:14:55,452
So good, so good

119
00:14:55,532 --> 00:14:57,462
That I got you

120
00:15:40,472 --> 00:15:43,062
- Mr. Crumb?
- Yes?

121
00:15:44,742 --> 00:15:46,732
