220
00:22:38,822 --> 00:22:40,352
Exactly.

221
00:22:40,422 --> 00:22:44,482
- Isn't that a marabou muddler?
- Yes. Are you a fly fisherman?

222
00:22:44,562 --> 00:22:48,162
