723
01:03:51,592 --> 01:03:54,752
"So-called"?
See for yourself, butch.

724
01:03:57,532 --> 01:04:01,062
95, 96, 97, 98...

725
01:04:05,042 --> 01:04:06,972
- 99.
- Amazing.

726
01:04:13,712 --> 01:04:15,312
All right.

727
01:04:25,492 --> 01:04:28,022
Right on time. Eliot!

728
01:04:35,342 --> 01:04:39,432
This is Jennifer.
